content: पुष्ट {%<ab>p. p.</ab>%} [पुष्-क्त] {@--1@} Nourished, fed, reared, brought up. {@--2@} Thriving, growing, strong, fat. {@--3@} Tended, cared for. {@--4@} Rich, magnificently provided. {@--5@} Complete, perfect. {@--6@} Full-sounding, loud. {@--7@} Eminent. --ष्टः <ab>N.</ab> of Viṣṇu. --ष्टं {@--1@} Nourishment. {@--2@} Acquisition, gain (<ab>Ved.</ab>).
